{"tid":27277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水土步南亞惡霸蝦阿婆　勇漢抱不平捱打","createTime":"2016-12-07T08:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T18:35:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"224e65d77311a3b109756cc8e0f284a2e7de76a8","tid":27277,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:36:39.000Z","msg":"12月03日(六) 22:52更新 21:57建立 <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=mlgTEEQq0fcbdNU03PtHEKEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=8d7ed738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】深水埗一名在區內蝦蝦霸霸的高大南亞漢，昨日在福榮街欺凌一名食環署外判清潔女工，踢翻其手推車上的垃圾，目擊的市民喝止兼挺身阻擋，被南亞漢揮拳毆傷手臂，驚動途人報警。受欺凌的清潔女工事後猶有餘悸，待人流漸多時才敢到該處清潔。 <br />\n<br />\n被南亞漢欺負的清潔女工姓周（70歲），人稱周婆婆。昨日早上近8時，一名身高約1點8米、穿T恤牛仔褲及戴鴨舌帽的南亞漢，持酒樽在福榮街690號便利店門外飲酒，期間用腳大力踢向周婆婆的手推車，令上面的垃圾冧落地上。男街坊伍先生聽到寓所樓下傳來嘈吵聲，落樓後見周婆婆圖趕走南亞漢，惟對方兇神惡煞圖出手打婆婆。 <br />\n<br />\n伍趨前了解，欲用身體隔開南亞漢與婆婆，詎料，南亞漢乘機出手打了他數拳，他用右前臂抵擋未有還手。此時，一名男途人發現南亞漢動粗上前了解，伍立即着他報警，南亞漢聞訊隨即拔足逃走。警員接報到場後，於大廈搜索南亞漢無果。 <br />\n<br />\n伍先生右前臂受傷，因當日趕上班關係，拒絕送院治療，後日到警署落口供。他指涉案南亞漢疑曾用酒淋潑女士及在梯間手淫嚇壞女住客。警方經調查後列作普通襲擊案，正追緝在逃南亞漢下落。 <br />\n<br />\n周婆婆憶述事件猶有餘悸，坦言：「當時梗係驚啦﹗佢咁高大又後生，打死你都有之喎如果蠻起上嚟﹗佢打你咪打你，野蠻人嚟架。」她又指街坊亦知該南亞漢不時騷擾別人，故「見到佢都掉頭走」，惟她因要工作則避無可避，現時只能待福榮街的舖頭開門，人流漸多時她才到該處清潔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_01p.jpg?20161204182225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20161204182225&h=9a9773b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有清潔女工昨日在深水埗被南亞漢欺凌，伍生(小圖)抱不平捱打。(劉子文/林兆崙攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_02p.jpg?20161204182225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20161204182225&h=c289da9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伍生指出案發位置。(林兆崙攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_03p.jpg?20161204182225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20161204182225&h=43acbfbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抱不平的伍先生指涉案南亞漢逃入一棟唐樓。(林兆崙攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_04p.jpg?20161204182225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20161204182225&h=72b488ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伍先生右手臂受傷。(林兆崙攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_05p.jpg?20161204182225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20161204182225&h=f391eded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南亞漢早前曾在梯間作猥瑣行為。(林兆崙攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_06p.jpg?20161204182225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20161204182225&h=ab8f44c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周婆婆會待福榮街的舖頭開門才到該處清潔。(黃永健攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_07p.jpg?20161204182225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001_07p.jpg%3F20161204182225&h=2aaa21e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fbkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001.html&d=mlgTEEQq0fcbdNU03PtHEKEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=c81f0eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/bkn-20161203215709781-1203_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cc0d80873b9a12f97409179bc8241e6ff5892951","tid":27277,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:44:48.000Z","msg":"蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dd970456d4be20d1b19333d1e434fb9d7a2003","tid":27277,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"作為一個瘦撚佢都算勇"},{"pid":"3da396f5f8cbe45b7168027c8cfa493510c794e2","tid":27277,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲蝻亞狗<br />\n比人溶左應該都無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cd3971f50a4e29dfc5d3c4da795f9a4592bff6","tid":27277,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:47:22.000Z","msg":"食綜援飲酒蝦蝦霸霸幾撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c2f621f8bbb383aaa40418f09e4d2c2469ccb4","tid":27277,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"土步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6316cdcfe115a8ac5e3ef8a3f1302574df93c8","tid":27277,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:51:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作為一個瘦撚佢都算勇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曹星如夠瘦啦，一樣可以一拳打到你入ICU"},{"pid":"7f9cde32df3d8daf38d351ec1f2ae5f0b149e8d5","tid":27277,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>作為一個瘦撚佢都算勇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曹星如夠瘦啦，一樣可以一拳打到你入ICU</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi